Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.78,0:00:19.74,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希望你去问问大家的意见以后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.77,0:00:22.07,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再由你来提案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:22.98,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}对你来说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.01,0:00:25.17,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这种经验也是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.19,0:00:26.31,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}能拜托你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:27.52,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.55,0:00:29.08,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}菲洛会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.10,0:00:30.82,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}交给你了喔 菲洛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.24,0:00:32.11,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.88,0:02:04.89,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}咦 还有学园祭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:06.43,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}听说是有的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.46,0:02:08.47,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}罗兹亲老师真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:10.17,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这么重要的事竟然都没说…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.20,0:02:12.16,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以 希望各班派出成员
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.18,0:02:13.23,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}来演话剧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.25,0:02:16.16,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是的 大家喜欢什么样的故事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.18,0:02:18.35,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯…喜欢的故事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:21.16,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在下的话 想要看安兹大人的故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:22.79,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要在身为女神的我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.82,0:02:24.08,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}演不死族的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.11,0:02:25.57,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不可以 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.59,0:02:26.99,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}话说 你也赞同过头了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.73,0:02:30.35,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊 黑暗骑士君要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:29.03,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\an8}又来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.27,0:02:30.83,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等等 阿克娅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.28,0:02:32.96,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你要自称女神也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.98,0:02:35.15,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是也要稍微再合群一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.18,0:02:36.63,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}才不是自称女神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:37.97,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}人家真的是女神啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:41.12,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然你的态度让人很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.15,0:02:42.98,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不过安兹大人有交代过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:45.17,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要温柔地对待傲娇的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:47.07,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:49.60,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}阿克娅是傲娇的人对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.62,0:02:52.32,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}像是对喜欢的人无法坦率之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:55.24,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}阿克娅 从被小朋友说教那时开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.26,0:02:56.45,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你就已经输了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.02,0:02:57.50,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.25,0:02:59.58,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\an8}啊 黑暗骑士君又回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:00.59,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:04.19,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}总之 再多去问问其他人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.21,0:03:05.98,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 菲洛会这样做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:07.07,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:13.00,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}骸骨的…哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:13.98,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}叔…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:15.38,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}骸骨的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.41,0:03:16.50,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还真拼命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.62,0:03:17.58,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我是安兹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:18.52,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:20.40,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}找我有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:22.63,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那个呢 现在菲洛正在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:24.92,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}询问大家的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:25.95,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.75,0:03:28.55,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喔 是话剧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:32.67,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 仓助说了想看不死族的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:34.55,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.57,0:03:35.13,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:37.81,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}让大家知道安兹大人的英勇事迹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.84,0:03:42.00,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}正好和至高的学园祭的主题相符合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:43.21,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:44.47,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}至于皇后的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:45.57,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}当然就是我夏提雅啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:46.65,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:48.11,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你这臭鳗鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.13,0:03:49.85,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:51.29,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你才是大嘴猩猩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:52.63,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们两个都冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.66,0:03:53.36,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:54.74,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真有默契
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:58.43,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}菲洛啊 虽然有些抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:00.96,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但我们对这种东西并不是很懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.98,0:04:04.04,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以你还是找别人讨论比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:05.58,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}例如说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:06.60,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:08.94,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}和真他们如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:11.68,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Explosion
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:17.35,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:18.37,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:21.29,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}火力击中在一点 威力强劲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:23.55,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也减少了对周围的伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:25.40,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还算是不错的爆裂魔法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:27.15,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么你觉得几分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:28.25,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}40分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:29.67,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果不能缩短咏唱时间的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.69,0:04:31.90,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在战场上要活用是很困难的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.93,0:04:34.25,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要缩短咏唱是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.28,0:04:36.31,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样看起来不就变得很逊了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:38.71,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}重要的是到发动为止的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:40.88,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}帅不帅这种事怎样都好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.91,0:04:42.13,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一点都不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:44.17,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不 在战场上一秒的延迟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.19,0:04:45.43,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}都可能决定生死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.46,0:04:47.22,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}把整个咏唱的内容给压缩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:48.48,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}用最短最快的方式来…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:48.48,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\an8}那个 谭雅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:49.51,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:51.99,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这家伙的咏唱是个谜喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.01,0:04:53.01,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:54.64,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我甚至不知道实际上这家伙的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:57.51,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}到底是不是真的需要咏唱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.53,0:04:59.43,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为她每次咏唱的内容都不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:01.79,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我如果不帅气的咏唱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:02.77,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是会死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:03.64,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们这群家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:05.35,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是在耍我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.37,0:05:06.38,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你这家伙才是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:07.42,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}到底打算做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:09.17,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好吃吗 菲洛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:10.81,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:14.51,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还满困难的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:17.04,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大家说的内容都不太一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.07,0:05:18.13,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:20.43,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊 是2班的大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:23.21,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你看起来超级烦恼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:24.32,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}发生什么事情了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:27.66,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那个呢 菲洛在想主题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:28.86,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}主题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:31.50,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 这次的学园祭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:34.42,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}菲洛我们要演话剧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:36.72,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在学园祭…演话剧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.74,0:05:40.59,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}菲洛被拜托去寻找要演的主题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:44.47,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯嗯 所以才像这样到处问大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.79,0:05:48.50,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是好难 因为大家说的都不一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:49.42,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:50.88,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}去图书馆如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:52.98,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那里有超级多的书
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.01,0:05:56.35,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我想里面一定会有你有兴趣的故事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:57.99,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}图书馆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:05:59.15,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.71,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谢谢你 大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:03.53,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是个好孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:05.21,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真的是个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:07.41,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}话虽如此 学园祭的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.43,0:06:09.48,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我还是第一次听罗兹瓦尔说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:11.06,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要再找时间好好问问才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:12.91,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是啊 不过帕克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:13.85,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:14.87,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:17.26,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要叫罗兹瓦尔老师才对喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.28,0:06:18.28,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:21.00,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那…那本书的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:22.53,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为很好理解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:25.03,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}应该能成为话剧的灵感才对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.62,0:06:28.57,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}来吧 拿到书就快点回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:29.37,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.39,0:06:31.87,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}回去叫主人读给菲洛听吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:33.94,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谢谢你 马雷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:36.19,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还有碧翠…碧翠子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:37.83,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我才不是碧翠子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:38.98,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那就再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:42.38,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是失礼的小姑娘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.56,0:06:49.74,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}方便问一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:51.14,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:52.56,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么…了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.73,0:06:54.73,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然不是什么重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:56.06,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不过你们还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:58.67,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}自己是怎么来到这所学园的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.69,0:07:00.13,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}听安兹大人说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.16,0:07:02.56,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是因为按下了按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:06.28,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然安兹大人说了是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.31,0:07:07.84,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}并和我们道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:09.53,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是我觉得伟大的至尊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:12.20,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一定是有什么考量的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:12.95,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:15.17,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}…信赖的人就在自己身边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:16.85,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还真是幸福的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:19.56,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}碧翠丝小姐没有这样的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:22.63,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}现在已经没有了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:24.50,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那个…昴先生之类的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:25.38,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:27.26,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可是一点能让人相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:28.56,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要素都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.58,0:07:30.30,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是…是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:31.84,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是这样啦 哼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:36.27,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喔 你拿的是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:38.65,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊 是狼姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:41.36,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是啊 我是狼姐姐喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:43.19,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我是现在对菲洛拿着的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.22,0:07:45.23,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}充满了兴趣的姐姐喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:46.33,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:47.68,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是为了要决定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:49.95,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}学园祭话剧主题借的书喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:50.69,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.71,0:07:53.39,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯嗯 这个怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:54.62,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}看起来很可怜的鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:56.69,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}被眼神凶恶的男人所引诱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:57.40,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}然后捉去做成烤鸡肉串的故事如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:07:59.43,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不要随便乱编故事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:02.34,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊 是黑发的大姐姐们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:03.79,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}露普你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:05.66,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}安兹大人应该已经命令过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:07.83,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要遵守学园生活的规则对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.85,0:08:10.61,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是啊 就只是想试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:12.53,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那种灰色地带嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:15.97,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你 我记得是叫做菲洛对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:18.88,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你在寻找一班话剧的主题是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:21.62,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 然后想着说不定能成为线索
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:24.78,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}从马雷和碧翠子那边借了书来看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:25.83,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}马雷大人吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:26.88,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.72,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那我们就一起帮你想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:30.37,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那就 看起来很可怜的狸猫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:32.02,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}被眼神凶恶的男人所引诱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:33.86,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}然后捉去做烤狸猫串呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:33.86,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\an8}这段刚刚用过了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.90,0:08:37.32,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是普通故事的话实在是太无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:39.40,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而且也是叫我们来演
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:40.35,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:41.69,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而且小娜要演白萝卜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:43.05,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}白萝卜是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.07,0:08:44.30,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}痛痛痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:47.38,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不过的确 如果要演的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.41,0:08:49.30,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}能够以最自然的状态来演是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.33,0:08:50.77,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}小娜最自然的状态的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:52.81,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不就只能让你演虐杀大王了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.83,0:08:55.03,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虐杀大王是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:56.15,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}各位小姐们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:57.78,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们在聊些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.46,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在聊和你们没有关系的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:00.49,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这些垃圾蛆虫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:02.32,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}长了一副漂亮的样子 但真恐怖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:03.03,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:04.28,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就算被你们这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:05.61,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}又臭又丑的虫给称赞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.63,0:09:07.39,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也一点都高兴不起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.41,0:09:08.91,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}小娜 就是那个!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.95,0:09:11.85,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是丑小鸭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:12.92,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}丑小鸭的兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:15.22,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是一直对它恶言相向吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.25,0:09:16.09,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果是那个角色的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:18.65,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}小娜就可以用最自然的状态来演了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:20.41,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}确实 根据不同的对象…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:22.78,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}很适合横行霸道的小娜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:24.86,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你说谁横行霸道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:25.85,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\an8}痛痛痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.97,0:09:28.11,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}丑小鸭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:29.21,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:30.08,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:31.25,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大姐姐们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:32.78,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还有叔叔们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:35.33,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯嗯 叔叔也…我不是叔叔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:35.33,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\an8}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:37.44,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}…平静的生活着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:39.04,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}剧终
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.54,0:09:40.58,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么样呢 菲洛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.61,0:09:43.00,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 菲洛喜欢这个故事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:43.99,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}尚文大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:45.53,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个超棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:46.62,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就演这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:48.13,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有这么喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.16,0:09:49.58,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是的 非常喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:51.52,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}确实是个好故事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:53.35,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}知道原来真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:55.77,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是非常高贵的存在之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:57.69,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为什么要看着我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:09:59.97,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么样呢 菲鲁特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:01.93,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.07,0:10:05.79,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好 那就决定一班
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.82,0:10:07.66,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要演出丑小鸭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.68,0:10:08.87,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.89,0:10:12.20,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}主人 菲洛好好努力过了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:13.73,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.76,0:10:14.61,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}欸嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:15.81,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}尚文大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:17.69,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我也想要您的称赞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:18.69,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.71,0:10:20.66,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}下次就麻烦拉芙塔莉雅做代表吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:23.89,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是的 请不要把我当小孩子啦
